          <title>Plan for $20 million firefighter training center near the site of Ohio derailment revived</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Norfolk Southern railroad worked with the state of Ohio and Youngstown State University to revive plans for a $20 million first responder training center near the site of the worst derailment in a decade in East Palestine, Ohio.]]></description>
